detaileddescription.para: Generic version of drone_model_acados_create which allows to use a different number of shooting intervals than the number used for code generation. If new_time_steps=NULL and n_time_steps matches the number used for code generation, the time-steps from code generation is used.
Update the time step vector. Number N must be identical to the currently set number of shooting nodes in the nlp_solver_plan. Returns 0 if no error occurred and a otherwise a value other than 0.
This function is used for updating an already initialized solver with a different number of qp_cond_N.
